Ultimate Beverage, South Africa’s premium boutique beverage experience, is a one-day trade exhibition followed by a two-day consumer exhibition, showcasing the finest local craft and small-batch producers. Ultimate Beverage will be hosted by Cape Town International Convention Centre from 28 – 29 January 2021. Visitors will have the opportunity to taste and purchase the wide selection of beverages on offer, as well as learn about the different techniques used in creating the ultimate flavour combinations in these small-batch products. Tickets available via Quicket